import java.util.*;
class Reversestring
{
public static void main(String args[])
{
Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
System.out.print("Enter data:");
String str=sc.nextLine();
StringBuilder sb=new StringBuilder(str);
System.out.print(sb.reverse());
}
}

output:
D:\coding>javac Reversestring.java

D:\coding>java Reversestring
Enter data:java is the best coding language
egaugnal gnidoc tseb eht si avaj
D:\coding>
